CHAPTER ______
1 AN ACT concerning
2 State Procurement – Exceptions – Historic Preservation Services
3 (The Honorable Barrie S. Ciliberti Historic Preservation Act of 2026)
4 FOR the purpose of establishing certain exceptions to State procurement requirements for
5 certain contracts with nonprofit entities related to historic preservation service
6 opportunities; requiring certain historic preservation, archaeology, and conservation
7 service contracts to include certain clauses; and generally relating to State
8 procurement and historic preservation services.
9 BY repealing and reenacting, with amendments,
10 Article – State Finance and Procurement
11 Section 11–203(a)(1)(xviii) and (xix)
12 Annotated Code of Maryland
13 (2021 Replacement Volume and 2025 Supplement)
EXPLANATION: CAPITALS INDICATE MATTER ADDED TO EXISTING LAW.
